# ============================================================
# ERA5-guided stratified sampling dataset builder (REVISED)
# - Output NPZ format unchanged: X, y, channels, used_cities, note
#
# Key upgrades vs your draft:
#  1) Categorical LC uses nearest resampling (no averaging)
#  2) Water-dominated ERA5 cells are dropped by WATER_FRAC_THR (coarse-cell water fraction)
#  3) Urban core NTL mask uses city-specific quantile (brightest 90%)
#  4) Stricter sample validity mask: requires target + core predictors finite
#
# Still:
#  - One fine pixel per ERA5(0.1°) cell (reduces pseudo-replication)
#  - Coastal-safe (does not hard-drop whole coastal cities; only water-dominated coarse cells)
#  - Fast vectorized reshape for block selection; minimal loops over usable blocks
# ============================================================

